{"tid":343821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊港男愈黎愈廢","createTime":"2017-08-01T18:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T06:15:29.000Z","uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a297db0e68a3c99e04b0d3635b2f3d3ef5af11eb","tid":343821,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:50:44.000Z","msg":"港男係指一群廢物物種 唔係泛指香港男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我早排有個朋友 識左一年幾<br />\n 之前就一直不斷同我講搞要一壇野啦 <br />\n咁好 我就話同佢搞 仲搵埋佢個朋友 諗住做好成件事 <br />\n佢個朋友就不斷ban人條橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但自己就乜都唔諗 要人砌個成品比佢食落肚咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都算啦 佢只係搵返黎幫手 <br />\n<br />\n我個朋友先最精采 明明係自己帶頭話要搞<br />\n玩失蹤 whatsapp唔睇唔覆 要人問候全家先話唔想再搞<br />\n無心搞起初就咪搵人幫 同曬出面d人差唔多傾好突然玩野 港男比人笑唔係無原因 就係多得呢種人"},{"pid":"fb9eaa8ae2374692cac4b769f0fd53583f77a58f","tid":343821,"uid":27960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:09:07.000Z","msg":"點樣可以因為你啲frd on9而得出港男廢嘅結論呢？<br />\n<br />\n定只係因爲你on9 合作啲partner都on99咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2964aefcf01aec9173a9ecc77cd1db69da746c6a","tid":343821,"uid":79502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"亂咁落定義"},{"pid":"19365f736ca730de6b9012accce2b1312a347db3","tid":343821,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:53:03.000Z","msg":"近排興踩低港男？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353dfbb62075bb8e16267a5d61e25c4244365a74","tid":343821,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排興踩低港男？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇睇第一句 港男係講緊一班唔成熟嘅廢青 唔係指全部人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}